{"tid":883660,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【B1頭條】美聯裁員 中原蝕1億 今次真係股樓齊爆!?","createTime":"2018-10-31T04:15:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T06:44:09.000Z","uid":28860,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"10fb926a0de099075b561743ca96196c72d04053","tid":883660,"uid":28860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:15:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">樓市步入嚴冬，本港兩大龍頭代理中原地產及美聯物業，面臨裁員危機。美聯先行向業績最差的100名員工開刀，部份人即時被炒，另外近一半員工須被迫自行放無薪假3個月。中原本月恐蝕逾1億元，為集團歷來虧損最高一個月，該行估計今次樓市嚴冬，恐多達6,000名代理失飯碗。</span><br />\n<br />\n現有約4,000名代理的美聯率先瘦身，昨向員工發通告，名為「bottom榜放取無薪假期機制」。「bottom榜」是指集團佣金收入最低的100名地產代理，集團已沿用多年。機制包括業績最差10%員工必須離職，涉10人﹔其後55%員工必須自行申請放無薪假期最少三個月。而榜內業績最高35%員工可由主管擔保。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181031/58856162\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181031%2F58856162&d=8px2%2Fe9R3OJ8fqB58kdGNL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=bde91cbc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181031%2F58856162&h=69daaa8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181031/58856162</a>"},{"pid":"d5876fdb6220524a2757c29000123275e124502f","tid":883660,"uid":8048,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:17:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/zh.uncyclopedia/images/f/f1/%E6%88%91%E6%83%B3%E9%96%8B%E9%A6%99%E6%AA%B3%E6%85%B6%E7%A5%9D.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20081212103438\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fzh.uncyclopedia%2Fimages%2Ff%2Ff1%2F%25E6%2588%2591%25E6%2583%25B3%25E9%2596%258B%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25AA%25B3%25E6%2585%25B6%25E7%25A5%259D.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20081212103438&h=a8d7f1b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb66e3b2a73e2658abeaaa8dbd3e102d699de7bf","tid":883660,"uid":106247,"like":